The main metropolitan areas of the Iberian Peninsula are [[Madrid metropolitan area|Madrid]], [[Barcelona metropolitan area|Barcelona]], [[Lisbon Metropolitan Area|Lisbon]], [[Valencia metropolitan area|Valencia]], [[Greater Metropolitan Area of Porto|Porto]], [[Seville metropolitan area|Seville]], [[Bilbao metropolitan area|Bilbao]], [[Ave (intermunicipal community)|Guimarães]], [[Málaga metropolitan area|Málaga]], [[Cávado (intermunicipal community)|Braga]], [[Central Asturias metropolitan area|Central Asturias]] (Gijón-Oviedo-Avilés), [[Alicante-Elche-Elda|Alicante-Elche]], [[Murcia metropolitan area|Murcia]] and [[Região de Coimbra|Coimbra]].

